        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n  /* PROBLEM SECTION - CONVERSION-OPTIMIZED (CONSISTENT STYLE) */\n  .lunanord-editorial {\n    background: #FFFFFF;\n    padding: 100px 40px;\n    border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB;\n  }\n\n  .lunanord-editorial-container {\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 80px;\n    align-items: start;\n  }\n\n  /* LEFT - TEXT CONTENT */\n  .lunanord-content-wrapper {\n    padding-top: 20px;\n  }\n\n  /* Eyebrow Label - Pink accent (this is fine) */\n  .lunanord-eyebrow {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #F3C5D4;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 1.5px;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    display: block;\n  }\n\n  /* Main Headline - DARK to match other sections */\n  .lunanord-headline {\n    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n    font-size: 48px;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    color: #1a1d2e; /* Changed from pink to match your other sections */\n    line-height: 1.2;\n    margin-bottom: 32px;\n    letter-spacing: -0.5px;\n  }\n\n  /* Body Text */\n  .lunanord-body-text {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 17px;\n    color: #4B5563;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    margin-bottom: 24px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n  }\n\n  /* Bold key phrases for scannability */\n  .lunanord-body-text strong {\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #1a1d2e;\n  }\n\n  /* Numbered List */\n  .lunanord-problems-list {\n    list-style: none;\n    padding: 0;\n    margin: 32px 0;\n  }\n\n  .lunanord-problems-list li {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 16px;\n    color: #4B5563;\n    padding: 14px 0;\n    padding-left: 36px;\n    position: relative;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6;\n  }\n\n  .lunanord-problems-list li:last-child {\n    border-bottom: none;\n  }\n\n  .lunanord-problems-list li::before {\n    content: attr(data-number);\n    position: absolute;\n    left: 0;\n    top: 14px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #F3C5D4; /* Pink accent on numbers is fine */\n    font-size: 15px;\n  }\n\n  /* Quote Block */\n  .lunanord-quote {\n    border-left: 4px solid #F3C5D4; /* Pink accent is fine */\n    padding-left: 24px;\n    margin: 32px 0;\n    background: #FAFAFA;\n    padding: 24px;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n  }\n\n  .lunanord-quote p {\n    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n    font-size: 20px;\n    font-style: italic;\n    color: #1a1d2e;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n    margin: 0 0 8px 0;\n  }\n\n  .lunanord-quote-attribution {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: #6B7280;\n    font-style: normal;\n  }\n\n  /* Stats Callout */\n  .lunanord-stat {\n    background: #F9FAFB;\n    border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    padding: 20px;\n    margin: 32px 0;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  .lunanord-stat-number {\n    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n    font-size: 42px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #F3C5D4; /* Pink accent on stat number is fine */\n    line-height: 1;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n\n  .lunanord-stat-label {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #6B7280;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n\n  /* RIGHT - IMAGES GRID */\n  .lunanord-image-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    gap: 24px;\n  }\n\n  /* Image Card */\n  .lunanord-image-card {\n    position: relative;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n  }\n\n  .lunanord-image-card img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: auto;\n    display: block;\n    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;\n    object-fit: cover;\n    filter: brightness(0.95);\n    border-radius: 8px;\n  }\n\n  /* Caption */\n  .lunanord-caption-minimal {\n    margin-top: 12px;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 8px;\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #6B7280;\n    font-weight: 500;\n  }\n\n  /* Status Indicator Dot */\n  .lunanord-dot {\n    width: 8px;\n    height: 8px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n  }\n\n  .dot-red { background: #EF4444; }\n  .dot-green { background: #10B981; }\n\n  /* Responsive */\n  @media (max-width: 968px) {\n    .lunanord-editorial {\n      padding: 60px 24px;\n    }\n\n    .lunanord-editorial-container {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      gap: 50px;\n    }\n\n    .lunanord-headline {\n      font-size: 36px;\n    }\n\n    .lunanord-image-grid {\n      order: -1;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<!-- EDITORIAL PROBLEM SECTION - CONVERSION OPTIMIZED -->\n<section class=\"lunanord-editorial\">\n  <div class=\"lunanord-editorial-container\">\n    \n    <!-- LEFT: Argument Structure -->\n    <div class=\"lunanord-content-wrapper\">\n      <span class=\"lunanord-eyebrow\">The Problem</span>\n      \n      <h2 class=\"lunanord-headline\">You're not failing. Your sleep environment is.</h2>\n\n      <p class=\"lunanord-body-text\">\n        If you lie awake for <strong>1-2 hours replaying tomorrow's to-do list</strong>, you're not broken. Your sleep is failing because of <strong>two things working against you simultaneously</strong>—and most solutions only address one.\n      </p>\n\n      <!-- The Dual Mechanism (Installs Belief #2) -->\n      <ul class=\"lunanord-problems-list\">\n        <li data-number=\"1.\">\n          <strong>Ambient light hijacks melatonin production.</strong> Even a sliver of light from streetlamps, your partner's phone, or early sunrise disrupts your brain's ability to produce the hormone that makes you sleepy.\n        </li>\n        <li data-number=\"2.\">\n          <strong>Racing thoughts activate your nervous system.</strong> Without an external calming signal, your brain stays in \"alert mode\"—replaying embarrassing moments, running through your to-do list, refusing to switch off.\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n\n      <p class=\"lunanord-body-text\">\n        Standard silk masks block <em>some</em> light but do nothing for your racing mind. Weighted blankets calm your nervous system but are <strong>too hot</strong> and let light leak in. Melatonin supplements address neither root cause.\n      </p>\n\n      <!-- Customer Quote (Real Voice from Research) -->\n      <div class=\"lunanord-quote\">\n        <p>\"I lie awake for hours replaying every embarrassing thing I've ever said. I've tried everything—melatonin, apps, weighted blankets. Nothing worked.\"</p>\n        <p class=\"lunanord-quote-attribution\">— Sarah M., Luna Nord customer</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- The Insight -->\n      <p class=\"lunanord-body-text\">\n        That's why Luna Nord addresses <strong>both mechanisms</strong>: 100% blackout blocks the light stealing your melatonin + gentle, evenly-distributed pressure signals your parasympathetic nervous system to rest. Not a heavy blanket. Not a flimsy mask. Both solutions, one tool.\n      </p>\n\n      <!-- Stat Callout (Social Proof) -->\n      <div class=\"lunanord-stat\">\n        <div class=\"lunanord-stat-number\">87%</div>\n        <div class=\"lunanord-stat-label\">\n          of women report falling asleep <strong>faster</strong> with Luna Nord within 3 nights\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- RIGHT: Visual Proof (Before/After) -->\n    <div class=\"lunanord-image-grid\">\n      \n      <!-- Before: The Problem -->\n      <div class=\"lunanord-image-card\">\n        <img \n          src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0953/1329/7782/files/Nimeton_malli_51.png?v=1767349601\" \n          alt=\"Woman struggling with insomnia - light pollution and racing thoughts\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        >\n        <div class=\"lunanord-caption-minimal\">\n          <span class=\"lunanord-dot dot-red\"></span>\n          Light leaks + racing thoughts = no sleep\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- After: The Solution -->\n      <div class=\"lunanord-image-card\">\n        <img \n          src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0953/1329/7782/files/Nimeton_malli_52_22ee4c04-b2dc-4349-b1e5-b431c195801a.png?v=1767365355\"\n          alt=\"Woman sleeping peacefully with Luna Nord weighted sleep mask\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        >\n        <div class=\"lunanord-caption-minimal\">\n          <span class=\"lunanord-dot dot-green\"></span>\n          100% blackout + gentle pressure = instant calm\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>",
